content: The energy in NYC is electric. Just got back and already feel the buzz. And my favorite bodega on the corner is still there, serving the best egg and cheese on a roll.
Joined a meetup at a local tech hub. Lots of talk about AI in finance. Feeling inspired and out of my depth at the same time.
Spent the morning reviewing my trading algorithms. It's like trying to teach an old dog new tricks, but with code.
My birthday was a quiet affair. Had some friends over, reflected on the year. Realized how much I've learned, and how much more there is to go.
Set up a meeting with a quant trader I met at the tech hub. Going to discuss potential mentorship opportunities.
